{
  "stem": "20609.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But the currency was set, the value of certain things and camp was set on-- on-- on cigarettes and dollars.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So now I get the letter and I find out for the first time my father is alive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So he also found me to the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Within a short time, I get a letter from my father's cousin in the United States.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Her name was Sabina Miller.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And she asked me if I would like to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Oh, by the way, I got that letter before I heard from my father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So now I-- I-- that was-- so I said, yes, I would love to go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So within a very short time, I-- I was sent-- I got an affidavit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Matter of fact, I think that was like within 30 or 90 days, like in June of '45, like a month or so afterwards, she sends me the affidavit from another relative of ours who was very rich, had a bunch of department stores.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "His there was Sam-- Samuel Jonas.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he owned like 16 department stores in New York and New York City, right on 14th Street.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I went-- so now-- [DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--I get the-- I get the affidavit, I rush it down to the American embassy in Copenhagen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at that time, I couldn't understand-- we had a-- we had a joke about-- about those three survivors who talk about where would you like to go?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the first guy, I'm going to Canada and the other guy says, I'm going to Australia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the third guy says, doesn't anybody want to go to the United States?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then one guy says, well, they have a new way of getting you in there.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
